<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
	<title>Confirm your FirstTouch account</title>
	<style type="text/css">

@media (min-width: 500px) {
  .button,
	.ft-button{
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: block;
    margin: 5px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 300;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 7px 12px 6px 12px;
    width: 250px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    background-color: #439042;
    border: solid 2px #439042;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 12px #666;
    text-align: center;
  }

  footer li {
    display: inline-block !important;
    margin-right: 20px !important;
  }

  .mt3-lg {
    margin-top: 30px !important;
  }

  .mb3-lg {
    margin-bottom: 30px !important;
  }

  .mt4-lg {
    margin-top: 40px !important;
  }

  pre {
    font-size: 14px !important;
  }
  .body {
    font-size: 14px !important;
    line-height: 24px !important;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 22px !important;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 16px !important;
  }
  small {
    font-size: 12px !important;
  }
}
</style>
</head>

<body class="body" style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Ubuntu, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: initial; max-width: 580px;">
	<header style="margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
    <p><%= image_tag(attachments['logo.png'].url) %></p>
	</header>

  <h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0;"> Hi First Name </h3>

  <p>
    You’re almost there. Our chief technology guy told me that we need to verify every sign up... something about security and keeping our network honest.
    If you’re anything like me, you probably won’t understand technology and how it works but I definitely wouldn’t want to be part of something that’s not authentic or valuable. And, I definitely don’t want my personal info compromised!
    So, what do we need you to do? Simple. Just click the link to verify your email address.
  </p>

	<p class="mt3-lg mb3-lg">
    <%= link_to("Confirm Email Address", confirm_account_path(@resource.confirmation_token), { class: "button ft-button", target: "_blank" }) %>
  </p>

  <p>
    Once you’re done, you can begin building your profile, expanding your professional Football network and scouting for talent.
    As one of the first users, I’m honestly, very excited to have you join the team! And, I would love to hear your thoughts, ideas and feedback once you’ve had a chance to play around on FirstTouch.
  </p>

  <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0;"> Welcome to FirstTouch.</p>
  <p>
    Matthew <br>
    CEO, FirstTouch <br>
    Message me on the platform or email me at matthew@firsttouch.io
  </p>

	<footer class="mt2 mt4-lg" style="border-top: 1px solid #D9D9D9; margin-top: 20px; padding: 20px 0;">
		<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding: 0;">
			<li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0;">
				<small style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #999;"><a href="https://firsttouch.io" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #E6E6E6; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">FirstTouch</a></small>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</footer>
</body>
